{"tid":1517152,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！91天水圍改左914","createTime":"2019-08-30T00:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T01:23:29.000Z","uid":6630,"like":355,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"9f5a3c105a592cb75247ac99c052a7c5f77c32a4","tid":1517152,"uid":6630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T00:10:46.000Z","msg":"<em><ins>代post</ins></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsG6WZR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsG6WZR.jpg&h=a42574a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家好，又係我呀，天水圍親子遊搞手。呢幾日收到好多人反映9月1日想全力和你塞。一開始我地認為因為兩個活動性質唔同，所以兩者不存在衝突。但始終兩個活動同時間進行，的確會影響到整體動員能力。<br />\n<br />\n我都好明白大家想集中人手，所以我地經過一輪熱烈討論之後，決定再次改期，改為9月14日（六），亦即係中秋節翌日。希望大家可以預留呢日比天水圍，比個機會我地做一次大型文宣，一齊爭取更多香港人支持。<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，對內嘅文宣傳單都係傳單/海報/連儂牆呢啲平面文宣，而今次嘅活動係希望透過活生生嘅遊行去解說及宣傳理念。雖然呢個係文宣性質嘅活動，但都希望大家積極參與，人數的確可以震撼人心。應承我，留返日比天水圍，好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n最後因為時間緊迫，希望大家盡力推post！話比全世界知，天水圍親子遊改咗9月14日！ 9月1日全力和你塞！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/BVNW9BX_iftvhSVVETZq7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FBVNW9BX_iftvhSVVETZq7A&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8v2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=6feb3610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/BVNW9BX_iftvhSVVETZq7A</a><br />\n<br />\n*不反對通知書待批"},{"pid":"4339f628cd647e82babe7710b4e8de66324cb582","tid":1517152,"uid":34489,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T00:12:22.000Z","msg":"支持 91全世界入機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0928d7204801346eaa4683d5eff30d3d088d08","tid":1517152,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T00:13:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e83574a55449f5eb61fea684434f8fef11fc93ae","tid":1517152,"uid":27647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T00:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6890cdd76ddd4201d0a5f4c1